videos.description: Jalen Knox hauls in 45-yard catch, setting up an easy touchdown run for Larry Rountree III.
videos.headline: Long catch sets up 1-yard Missouri TD run

videos.description: South Carolina's Michael Scarnecchia floats a 5-yard pass to Bryan Edwards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Scarnecchia lofts 5-yard TD pass

videos.description: Damarea Crockett powers his way in for 1-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Missouri pounds in second 1-yard TD

videos.description: Michael Scarnecchia and Bryan Edwards connect for the second time in the game for a 17-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: South Carolina's 2nd TD pass goes to Edwards

videos.description: Parker White gives South Carolina a lead with a 42-yard boot in a pouring rainstorm.
videos.headline: South Carolina hits long go-ahead field goal in heavy rain

videos.headline: Rountree leaps and scores Missouri TD
